spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_LINEAR_FLASH_SYNC_BURST
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Enable Sync Burst Mode For Numonyx Flash
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: This parameter should be set by the user when the targeted memory is Numonyx Flash and only when the flash is configured in Sync read mode.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_LFLASH_PERIOD_PS
spirit:parameter.spirit:displayName: Numonyx Sync Burst Flash Clock Period
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: This parameter should be set by the user when the targeted memory is Numonyx Flash and only when the flash is configured in Sync read mode.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_AXI_CLK_PERIOD_PS
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: User should provide the value here which is equivalent to AXI clock used. This value is used for internal callibration of counters when Asynchronous memories are used.
